Inkwell
=======

Inkwell is an Obsidian plugin for long-form writing, maintained by
Dwi Elfianto (https://github.com/delfianto).

It is derived from Longform, originally created by Kevin Barrett (kevboh):

    https://github.com/kevboh/longform

The Longform plugin architecture, compile pipeline, sidebar UX, and much of
the core functionality originated in that project. Inkwell has since diverged
with a rebuilt toolchain and a revised on-disk project schema, but a
substantial amount of the inherited code remains.

